The National Union of Road Transports Workers (NURTW), Ado/Igbesa branch, has congratulated the in-coming president of the union, Prof. Tajudeen Ibikunle Baruwa (Osunba of Ilogbo-Ota). In a statement jointly signed by the baale of Odan Agbara, Chief Waheed Fashina, and  Alhaji  Jimoh Fagunle (Alhaji White), members of the union said, given Baruwa’s track record as a renowned unionist and astute administrator, he had the experience to lead NURTW to greater heights.